geometry:

```json
{
  "axis": {
    "id": "pc1",
    "tickLabelPlacement": {
      "avoid": ["axis-spine"],
      "minGap": 5,
      "nudge": {"x": 8, "y": 7},
      "maxSteps": 6
    }
  }
}
```

3D axes with visible tick labels should also render visible tick marks unless
the source suppresses them. Store tick geometry as a projected tick anchor, a
